          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/p/Mayhem-Fight-Series-100087314049666/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-btn" title="Facebook">f</a>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mayhemfightseries/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-btn" title="Instagram">📷</a>
          <a href="https://www.eventbrite.com.au/o/mayhem-fight-series-57661453403" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-btn" title="Eventbrite">🎟</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="footer__heading">Quick Links</div>
        <ul class="footer__links">
          <li><a href="/events/">Events</a></li>
          <li><a href="/fighters/">Fighters</a></li>
          <li><a href="/results/">Results</a></li>
          <li><a href="/gallery/">Gallery</a></li>
          <li><a href="/community/">Community</a></li>
          <li><a href="/sponsors/">Sponsors</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="footer__heading">Get Involved</div>
        <ul class="footer__links">
          <li><a href="/contact/">Fighter Registration</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact/">Sponsorship Enquiry</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact/">Media Accreditation</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com.au/o/mayhem-fight-series-57661453403" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Buy Tickets</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com.au/o/mayhem-fight-series-57661453403" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch Livestream</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="footer__heading">Contact</div>
        <div class="footer__contact-line"><span>👤</span><span>John Halford — Promoter</span></div>
        <div class="footer__contact-line"><span>📞</span><span><a href="tel:0411648890" style="color:inherit;">0411 648 890</a></span></div>
        <div class="footer__contact-line"><span>📍</span><span>Newcastle, NSW, Australia</span></div>
        <div class="footer__contact-line"><span>🎟</span><span><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com.au/o/mayhem-fight-series-57661453403" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--red);">Tickets on Eventbrite</a></span></div>
